external libraries

1: Bundled under src/external_libs

- numerical_io by John Woodruffe (jpwoodruff@irisinternet.net) (licence unknown) 
  See: http://www.adapower.com/index.php?Command=Class&ClassID=AdaLibs&CID=460
- unzip_ada by G. de Montmollin (gdemont@users.sourceforge.net) (MIT Licence)
  See: http://unzip-ada.sourceforge.net/
- strings_edit V2.1 by Dmitry A. Kazakov (mailbox@dmitry-kazakov.de) (GPL Licence)
  See: http://www.dmitry-kazakov.de/ada/strings_edit.htm
- aunit 1.03 by Ed Falis (falis@adacore.com) (GPL Licence)
  see: https://libre.adacore.com/aunit/
  Note that this is not the current AUnit version. The current v2 version from Adacore is very different
  and won't work with the tests/ code.
  
  Thanks to all of these people and their fellow contributors.
  
2: Not Bundled

Ada web server (AWS) downloadable from https://libre.adacore.com/aws/

3: Dependencies on GNAT

- uses some Ada 2005 features & libraries, especially Ada.Containers
- some cases of XX'Img rather than <TYPE>'Image( XX )
- ?? Some pragmas ??

Build instructions under Windows:

http://j-paine.org/installing_aws_for_xp.html

